Package: TALEdesign
Type: Package
Title: Toxicity Adaptive Lists design (TALE) for Drug-Combination Phase I Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Francesco Mariani
Maintainer: Francesco Mariani <f.mariani@uniroma1.ir>
Description: The TALE design is a simple algorithm-based approach for phase-I dual-agent cancer trials. A R Shiny application based on this package is available at: https://6kp5ow-francesco-mariani.shinyapps.io/TALEdesign/.
             The main function of the package is "ConductTrial" which allows to specify the trial parameters and simulate the trial.
